The condition defines the economic boundary for positive deployment: a firm with higher organizational readiness can sustain positive deployment under a wider range of loss environments, while a firm facing very high breach-loss magnitude may find even modest AI deployment unprofitable. Assumption 2 excludes only the extreme case in which the gap is so severe that no deployment is worthwhile at any capability level.
