Appendix M Interpretation of the Damage Channel
The baseline reflects the gap: co-varies with authority exposure because governance has not constrained the combination. See Assumption 1 for the formal statement. -type organizational readiness investments raise productivity without expanding the damage channel, because they do not co-vary with authority exposure under gap conditions. Appendix N shows the paradox is robust to partial inclusion of in the damage channel.
